
# Commit message (use Conventional Commits format)
#
# <type>[optional scope]: <description>
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add config subcommand
#   fix(config): handle missing config file error
#   docs: update README with usage instructions
#   refactor: simplify download logic
#   test: add tests for config parser
#   chore: update dependencies
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore
#
# If the commit introduces a breaking change, add a line:
# BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#
# The body and footer are optional. Wrap lines at 72 characters.
#
